OL,3,CDerby 10k organisers confirm measuring
OL,4,Cerror led to race being around 400m
OL,5,Cshort
OL,7,FThe organiser of the 2026 Derby 10k
OL,8,Fhas admitted the run was around 400
OL,9,Fmetres too short after a number of
OL,10,Fcompetitors complained upon completing
OL,11,Ftheir race.
OL,13,FRunners competing in the race across
OL,14,Fthe city on Sunday (15 March)
OL,15,Fcomplained a shorter distance showed
OL,16,Fon their GPS devices.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
