PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773853860
OL,3,CDerby 10k organisers confirm measuring
OL,4,Cerror led to race being around 400m
OL,5,Cshort
OL,7,FAs a result, Derby County Community
OL,8,FTrust said the course required an
OL,9,Fofficial re-measure which was taken by
OL,10,Fa member of the Association of UK
OL,11,FCourse Measurers (AUKCM). The Trust
OL,12,Fsaid the subsequent review confirmed
OL,13,Fthe original official measurement
OL,14,Ftaken by AUKCM contained an error.
OL,16,FIn a statement on the Trust's website,
OL,17,FAUKCM said: "Following the Derby 10K
OL,18,Fon Sunday 15 March 2026, concerns were
OL,19,Fraised regarding the course distance.
OL,26,@yD@MOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773853860
OL,3,CDerby 10k organisers confirm measuring
OL,4,Cerror led to race being around 400m
OL,5,Cshort
OL,7,F"AUKCM carried out a verification
OL,8,Fmeasurement on 17 March, which
OL,9,Fconfirmed the course, as run, was
OL,10,Fapproximately 400 metres short.
OL,12,F"AUKCM acknowledges the error and the
OL,13,Fimpact on runners' results."
OL,15,FThere was also an error on the course
OL,16,Fmap, admitted by the Trust, which
OL,17,Fsuggested runners should have turned
OL,18,Faround at Ascot Drive. This was
OL,19,Fapologised for, but the Trust stressed
OL,20,Fit was not a contributor for the short
OL,21,Fcourse.
OL,26,@uD@\O]
