OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773853860
OL,3,CDerby 10k organisers confirm measuring
OL,4,Cerror led to race being around 400m
OL,5,Cshort
OL,7,FIt said: "Derby County Community
OL,8,FTrust, as race organisers, value AUKCM
OL,9,Fas a trusted and longstanding
OL,10,Fpartner, and we appreciate their
OL,11,Fwillingness to address the issue
OL,12,Fopenly.
OL,14,F"We recognise that mistakes can occur
OL,15,Fin any largescale event and we are
OL,16,Fgrateful for AUKCM's commitment to
OL,17,Fworking with us on corrective actions
OL,18,Fto ensure continued accuracy and
OL,19,Fintegrity."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
