OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1773853860
OL,3,CDerby 10k organisers confirm measuring
OL,4,Cerror led to race being around 400m
OL,5,Cshort
OL,7,FThe Trust added: "We share the
OL,8,Fdisappointment that this year's race
OL,9,Fdidn't meet our usual high standards
OL,10,Fand we are grateful for the
OL,11,Funderstanding and feedback we've
OL,12,Freceived from the running community."
